212	                        // If the pipe is already an object we'll just make a callable and pass it to
213	                        // the pipe as-is. There is no need to do any extra parsing and formatting
214	                        // since the object we're given was already a fully instantiated object.
215	                        $parameters = [$passable, $stack];
